---
import { EncryptedText } from "../ui/encrypted-text";
---

<section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8">
    <div class="mb-16">
      <span class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-mid-gray font-mono">
        <EncryptedText client:visible text="MISSION" />
      </span>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-display text-near-black leading-tight mb-12">
      Developing the Next Generation of National Security Innovators
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-16">
      <p class="text-dark-gray leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg">
        San Jose State sits at the center of Silicon Valley, surrounded by the companies and technologies reshaping national defense. The talent is here. What's been missing is the pipeline connecting that talent to the missions that need it most. NSIN at SJSU was founded to close that gap.
      </p>
      <p class="text-dark-gray leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg">
        We bring together students from engineering, computer science, policy, and business to work on the problems our country can't afford to ignore. Supply chain vulnerabilities, emerging threats, critical infrastructure, strategic competition. These challenges demand people from every discipline working together, and we're building that team at SJSU.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-l-2 border-near-black pl-8 py-4">
      <p class="font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-near-black leading-relaxed italic">
        "What would it look like to build a company that could take those bright people out of the advertising industry, out of the search engine optimization industry, out of the augmented reality mustache emoji industry, and put them to work on things that were more important."
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-mid-gray text-sm">
        Palmer Luckey, founder of Anduril Industries
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
